snippet.title: The Mosquito Gang - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
War...War never changes... Especially when it comes to the eternal battle between human and... mosquitoes. Try on the role of an insect exterminator or blood-thirsty small pests in a game with asymmetric multiplayer, where one human fights vs. four mosquitoes!
